Contextualize — has the strategic context shifted (market, competitive, organizational)?
Empathize — do you have fresh user/customer evidence, or are you running on stale empathy?
Synthesize — have you actually integrated what you learned this quarter into a coherent picture?
Hypothesize — what's the strongest untested assumption blocking the next move?
